import axios from "axios"; import React, { useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const endpoint = "http://localhost:8000/api/Hotel"; export default function CreateHotel() { const [NombreHotel, setNombreHotel] = useState(""); const [Direccion, setDireccion] = useState(""); const [Ciudad, setCiudad] = useState(""); const [Nit, setNit] = useState(); const [NumeroHabitaciones, setNumeroHabitaciones] = useState(); const [idhabitaciones, setidHabitaciones] = useState(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const store = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); await axios.post(endpoint, { NombreHotel: NombreHotel, Direccion: Direccion, Ciudad: Ciudad, Nit: Nit, NumeroHabitaciones: NumeroHabitaciones, idhabitacion: idhabitaciones, }); navigate("/"); }; return (
setNombreHotel(e.target.value)} type="text" className="form-control" id="validationDefault01" required />
setDireccion(e.target.value)} type="text" className="form-control" id="validationDefault02" required />
setCiudad(e.target.value)} type="text" className="form-control" id="validationDefault03" required />
setNit(e.target.value)} type="number" className="form-control" id="validationDefault04" required />
setNumeroHabitaciones(e.target.value)} type="number" className="form-control" id="validationDefault05" required />
setidHabitaciones(e.target.value)} type="number" className="form-control" id="validationDefault06" required />
); }
